Package: otel-dpu
Version: SED__DPU_AGENT_PKG_VERSION
Section: base
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Depends: jq
Maintainer: Forge team <swngc-forge-dev@nvidia.com>
Description: OpenTelemetry for site controller DPUs
 This package installs the OpenTelemetry collector and mTLS certs renewal
 agent. It expects a JSON file at /etc/site-dpu.json containing "site" and
 "domain" values and an array of "endpoints" in the form { "fqdn": "some.fqdn",
 "ip": "10.0.0.1" } including carbide api and otel ingress. A post-install
 script reads this file and updates /etc/hosts and sets hostname.
